Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.88,0:02:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,October of 1944. A landing party and a convoy fleet, \Nled by Field Marshal MacArthur, assembled in the Leyte Gulf.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.91,0:02:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The 2nd Fleet under Vice Admiral Kurita Takeo \Nwas dispatched on a mission to destroy this American Fleet.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.11,0:02:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Composed of the battleships Yamato, Musashi, Nagato,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.51,0:02:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,as well as the heavy cruiser Atago and various screens, \NJapan's crown fleet, numbering 39 ships,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.16,0:02:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,sortied from Brunei Bay in Borneo.
